  X-02,"Wizard → installer wiring gap — Phase 8 writes to repo skills/<name>/SKILL.md but installer writes to ~/.claude/skills/<name>/SKILL.md. No phase wires them. First-time author hits broken experience.",feature-coverage-agent,blocking
